OL,3,CMan charged after stabbing at Barry
OL,4,CIsland left boy needing leg amputated
OL,6,FA man has been charged following a
OL,7,Fstabbing on Barry Island that left a
OL,8,Fteenage boy needing his leg amputated.
OL,10,FSouth Wales Police confirmed 18-year-
OL,11,Fold Idris Ahmed, from Riverside,
OL,12,FCardiff, has been charged with
OL,13,Fwounding with intent and possession of
OL,14,Fa knife, or sharp pointed article in a
OL,15,Fpublic area.
OL,17,FThe incident took place on Bank
OL,18,FHoliday Monday (May 25).
