OL,3,CMan charged after stabbing at Barry
OL,4,CIsland left boy needing leg amputated
OL,6,FIt was later confirmed that a 17-year-
OL,7,Fold boy from Cardiff suffered a
OL,8,Fserious leg injury. He remains in
OL,9,Fcritical care at the University
OL,10,FHospital of Wales in Cardiff after
OL,11,Fundergoing a leg amputation.
OL,13,FAhmed was remanded in custody and
OL,14,Fappeared at Cardiff Magistrates' Court
OL,15,Fon Saturday, June 6.
